reviewText: This DVD was bought as a gift for my step-dad and he absolutely loves watching it , thank you so very much Amazon !

This is not what I expected.  This would be a great home movie or a video of watching your buddy shoot a hog.  If you are into hog hunting with dogs you might like a scene or two.  To be honest you will find much better on youtube.  I was looking for a video that was education as well as entertaining, and this one was neither.  I don't believe there was any real effort put into filming a real hunt.
This video has lots of great action. The hunts are very exciting and the action is non stop. If you enjoy hog hunting you will really like this video.
